    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you roll a Superiority Die, you can reroll it and take either result.</p><p>Additionally, when you use your Second Wind feature, you gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li>You regain one of your expended Superiority Die.</li><li>Your level of Exhaustion, if any, is reduced by 1.</li><li>You add double your Proficiency Bonus to any Strength, Dexterity or Constitution checks you make for the next minute.</li><li>Starting at 15th level, you regain one expended use of your Indomitable feature.</li></ul>",
